Description:
Help make libraries relocatable, that is, to allow them to function
properly when copied to an arbitrary directory.

Files:
doc/relocatable.texi
lib/relocatable.h
lib/relocatable.c
m4/relocatable-lib.m4

Depends-on:
xalloc

configure.ac:

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += relocatable.c

Include:
"relocatable.h"

License:
GPL

Maintainer:
Bruno Haible, Ben Pfaff

